### Get all data temperature and humidity
# GET http://10.28.129.153:5000/api/data
GET https://do-an-ktmt-backend.onrender.com/api/data


### Get data temperature and humidity latest
GET http://10.28.129.153:5000/api/data/sensors/latest


### Get data according sensors (humidity or temperature)
GET https://do-an-ktmt-backend.onrender.com/api/data/sensors?variable=humidity


### Get data according sensors and timestamps (humidity or temperature)
GET https://do-an-ktmt-backend.onrender.com/api/data/sensorToTime?variable=temperature&start_date=2024-09-01&end_date=2024-09-30


